<%# Full vote aggregate (RatingSummary): likes + difficulty meter side by side.
    Used on the show page under the byline; browse cards place the two pieces
    separately (likes by the byline, meter in the meta). Callers pass summary:
    (nil for unrated — renders nothing). %>
<% if summary %>
  <span class="m-ratemeta">
    <%= render "play/likes", summary: summary %>
    <%= render "play/difficulty_meter", summary: summary %>
  </span>
<% end %>
